Bash script that creates an IPv6 ad-hoc network.

Instructions:

	Download the script.
	Give it execute permission:
		#chmod +x ipv6Adhoc.sh
	Execute it with root permission
		#./ipv6Adhoc.sh

Notes: 
	Run the script on each computer that you want to connect.
	It's necesary that you use the same information on each computer, just change the IPv6 address.




